<plot>Maria and her husband are a middle-class couple that has to move in with the father of hers, who has a debilitating aneurism. The woman suffers from an obsolete existence as a submitting housewife. Her husband is extremely catholic and does not support the idea of sending Maria's father to an old people's home. She sees no escape from her torture, until a mysterious call takes place.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262661</url></doc>
